IV. The Semiotic Power Lifecycle

Pantheon recognizes the universal sequence:

Name ‚Üí Encode ‚Üí Legitimize ‚Üí Coordinate ‚Üí Empower
Empower ‚Üí Contradict ‚Üí Reframe ‚Üí Dissolve ‚Üí Rebuild


‚∏ª

Governance Use

All Pantheon mythic or symbolic constructs must include:
	‚Ä¢	Origin narrative
	‚Ä¢	Use scope
	‚Ä¢	Sunset or reinterpretation mechanism

This prevents symbolic constructs from becoming self-sealing authority engines.

